---
title: 图 3-1 调度组件协作关系图
---

flowchart TB
    subgraph KafkaIn["📥 Kafka 任务导入 Topic"]
        TaskTopic[(任务消息队列)]
    end

    subgraph Scheduler["⏱️ 任务调度层"]
        Importer["📥 任务导入器
(Task Importer)

职责: 消费 Kafka 消息
解析任务类型
写入数据库"]

        Runner["⚙️ 任务执行器
(Task Runner)

职责: 轮询 PENDING 任务
调用 AI Agent 执行
更新执行结果"]

        Cleaner["🧹 任务清理器
(Task Cleaner)

职责: 检测超时 RUNNING 任务
强制标记为 FAILED
释放执行资源"]

        Reporter["📤 任务报告器
(Task Reporter)

职责: 轮询已完成任务
发送到 Kafka 结果 Topic
更新报告状态"]
    end

    subgraph Database["🗄️ SQLite 数据库"]
        TaskTable[(任务表)]
    end

    subgraph KafkaOut["📤 Kafka 结果上报 Topic"]
        SuccessTopic[(成功 Topic)]
        FailedTopic[(失败 Topic)]
    end

    TaskTopic -->|消费消息| Importer
    Importer -->|写入新任务
状态: PENDING| TaskTable

    TaskTable -->|查询 PENDING| Runner
    Runner -->|状态更新
RUNNING → SUCCESS/FAILED| TaskTable

    TaskTable -->|检测超时| Cleaner
    Cleaner -->|状态更新
RUNNING → FAILED| TaskTable

    TaskTable -->|查询已完成
report_status: PENDING| Reporter
    Reporter -->|发送结果| SuccessTopic
    Reporter -->|发送结果| FailedTopic
    Reporter -->|更新状态
report_status: SUCCESS| TaskTable

    style Scheduler fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Runner fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2,stroke-width:3px
